I haven't played any computer games in ages.  I don't think I have any of mine currently loaded.  I know I have some like Zork and Myst.  I prefer my Nintendo and I like board games and card games as well.  I also like group type games.  Like the game &quot;Four on a couch&quot; and stuff like that.  I also love stuff like Miniature Golf, Air Hockey, Pool, Ping Pong, Bowling and stuff like that. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">**********************************************<br>
